articles.title: Ulsan equal Asian Champions League run in rain-affected win - Reuters
articles.description: Torrential rain could not stop title holders Ulsan Hyundai from equalling their record run of consecutive wins in the Asian Champions League when Hong Myung-bo's side defeated Thailand's BG Pathum United 2-0 in Bangkok on Wednesday.
